-- UBS’s Weber Says Dividends to Remain ‘Moderate’: SonntagsZeitung
-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 2012-08-19T07:26:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-19/ubs-s-weber-says-dividends-to-remain-moderate-sonntagszeitung.html
UBS AG Chairman  Axel Weber  said
shareholder dividends will initially remain “moderate,”
 SonntagsZeitung  reported.  UBS is devoting itself to coping with the past and building
capital over the next two years while the industry is in
“structural crisis,” Weber cited as saying in the Swiss
newspaper  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Geneva at 
